---
title: Creamy Chorizo & Leek Potato Top Pie with Baby Broccoli
description: Things are getting a bit heated in the kitchen when a mild chorizo is cooking in the pan with a variety of veg. Add a
bechamel tomato sauce in, cooked with leek and baby broccoli, to create a mouth-watering filling ready to be baked
under a potato mash topping. It’s a chorizo pie, baked, beautiful and ready to serve piping hot!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6481829838f49a2a03a2f03e-ecc9aee5.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/6481829838f49a2a03a2f03e.pdf
